document_title: Left-sided migraine: Causes, symptoms and prevention
subsection_content:
Symptoms of left migraine can be a warning sign of diseases that the patient should not ignore, such as:
Migraine headaches; Cerebrovascular malformations; Meningitis; Encephalitis; Glaucoma; Cold; Flu; Giant cell arteritis; Cluster headaches; Sinusitis; …
